Class DefaultValue

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.model.DefaultValue
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class DefaultValue extends Object implements Serializable
This class contains all the default values used in the project. These constants define various settings and parameters throughout the application.
